                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/aside/">黑甜</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar20 rating" title="较差"></span>
                    <span>2010-03-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">就像鬼佬写的书让他许知远直译成了中文，连书名都这么假洋鬼子。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
